Mixed-license directory.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

joins.yaml  →  AGPL-3.0-or-later  (../LICENSE-app)

The curated join registry between datasets — the bridges, normalization
rules, and key relationships — is licensed under AGPL-3.0. This is
domain knowledge that took significant work to compile, and is the
same license as the application that consumes it (portal/).

SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

datasets.yaml, sources.yaml, schemas/  →  CC-BY-4.0  (../LICENSE-data)

The dataset catalog (titles, descriptions, schemas, source URLs)
is metadata about public data and stays under CC-BY-4.0, like the
data it describes.

SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0

